gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Mavericks 118, 76ers 102
gameRecap.excerpt: The Mavericks defeated the 76ers, 118-102. Kyrie Irving put up 23 points (10-17 FG), five rebounds and eight assists for the Mavericks, while Luka Doncic added 19 points, eight rebounds and four 3PM in the victory. Kelly Oubre Jr. tallied 19 points and six rebounds for the 76ers in the losing effort. The Mavericks improve to 27-23 on the season, while the 76ers fall to 30-19.
